data.description: Welcome to 618 E 1st Street, a charming single-family sanctuary nestled in New Richmond Township, WI. This delightful residence offers 5 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms and 2,824 square feet of space, providing an inviting retreat. Step into a spacious haven where elegance meets practicality. The heart of the home, the kitchen, features ample space and expansive countertops. Enjoy the convenience of heated floors complementing the ease of one-level living. Beyond its interiors, this residence boasts a serene waterfront view of the Willow River. A vast .801-acre backyard invites privacy and room for personalization, creating a tranquil getaway. Convenience meets tranquility with a short drive to nearby shops and restaurants. Yet, despite it accessibility, this home offers a peaceful escape from the city's hustle and bustle. Picture evenings spent in your private oasis, hosting under the open sky or finding solace by the river's gentle flow.
